r.s: Classes that define complex numbers and their operations
r.d: Classes that represent and manipulate complex numbers. Contain definitions for basic arithmetic functions, as well as trigonometric, inverse trigonometric, hyperbolic, inverse hyperbolic, exponential and logarithms of complex numbers.
